fields.name: Original Watercolor Seascape Abstract Painting, Wall Art Abstract Art Purple.
fields.meta_desc: Original watercolor seascape abstract painting inspired by Irish landscapes, featuring vibrant purple tones on high-quality paper.
fields.details:
Original watercolor painting.

The painting is done with artist quality paints on 140 lb cold pressed, acid free watercolor paper.

Size: A5 - 148 x 210mm

This painting is inspired by the beautiful landscapes in the West of Ireland.

Please note that tones and colors may differ slightly according to the monitor or screen used for viewing the painting.

  • Signature at the front
  • The painting is not framed
  • It can be matted and framed
  • Shipping with tracking number
